It's the truth.

257
00:16:46.589 --> 00:16:49.151
Yeah. it's the truth.
so stop trying to protect me from it.

258
00:16:49.175 --> 00:16:52.405
- Well. then I'm gonna have to kill him.
- No.

259
00:16:52.429 --> 00:16:54.782
