- Right. it's a shit idea.

260
00:16:54.806 --> 00:16:57.118
You kill Kreshnik. his brother takes over.

261
00:16:57.142 --> 00:16:59.161
You kill the brother. the cousin
takes over. Kill the cousin.

262
00:16:59.185 --> 00:17:01.080
the fucking great grandma takes over.

263
00:17:01.104 --> 00:17:02.456
and on and on it goes.

264
00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:04.375
They'll hunt you down
for the rest of your life.

265
00:17:04.399 --> 00:17:07.420
No more killing.
That's not who you are anymore.

266
00:17:07.444 --> 00:17:08.963
Well. right. okay.

267
00:17:08.987 --> 00:17:10.238
- what about this then?
- Clara?

268
00:17:12.031 --> 00:17:14.575
- Clara?
- My God.

269
00:17:16.119 --> 00:17:17.680
I can't believe it...

270
00:17:17.704 --> 00:17:19.682
Arnando.

271
00:17:19.706 --> 00:17:21.058
- Beautiful!
- How are you?

272
00:17:21.082 --> 00:17:22.792
- Good. Good.
- Give me a kiss.

273
00:17:25.587 --> 00:17:27.398
She just...

274
00:17:27.422 --> 00:17:29.692
switched into a completely
different person.

275
00:17:29.716 --> 00:17:31.777
Obviously. she's undercover.

276
00:17:31.801 --> 00:17:33.070
So. be cool.

277
00:17:33.094 --> 00:17:34.822
It's been a while.

278
00:17:34.846 --> 00:17:36.014
Ever since...

279
00:17:36.431 --> 00:17:38.558
the death of Jean-Paul.

280
00:17:38.808 --> 00:17:40.268
What a tragedy. no?

281
00:17:44.439 --> 00:17:46.191
My God. I know who that is.

282
00:17:48.610 --> 00:17:50.695
He's a fucking arms dealer.

283
00:17:51.863 --> 00:17:53.299
Hello. how are you? Everything okay?

284
00:17:53.323 --> 00:17:55.593
No... He is English. She is American.

285
00:17:55.617 --> 00:17:58.429
I'm having a little party tonight
at my house.

286
00:17:58.453 --> 00:18:01.098
and it would be my honor
for you to join me.

287
00:18:01.122 --> 00:18:03.457
- Yes.
<i>- Sì?</i>

288
00:18:05.043 --> 00:18:07.629
I would love to show you my etchings.

289
00:18:12.091 --> 00:18:15.237
<i>- Ciao.
- Ciao. Ciao. bello.</i>

290
00:18:15.261 --> 00:18:16.739
Get up.

291
00:18:16.763 --> 00:18:18.908
We're leaving now.
We need to get out of Monaco.

292
00:18:18.932 --> 00:18:19.867
