293
00:18:19.891 --> 00:18:21.702
- I need a box for this.
- Shut up.

294
00:18:21.726 --> 00:18:23.019
Get up.

295
00:18:25.021 --> 00:18:27.625
- Who was that guy?
- Friend of an old target.

296
00:18:27.649 --> 00:18:31.545
- And by target. you mean...
- Yes. I killed his friend.

297
00:18:31.569 --> 00:18:33.822
But he was the head
of a human trafficking ring.

298
00:18:35.031 --> 00:18:36.926
Well. he certainly seemed
very taken with you.

299
00:18:36.950 --> 00:18:38.135
Shut up.

300
00:18:38.159 --> 00:18:40.137
He just invited you
to have a look at his etchings.

301
00:18:40.161 --> 00:18:42.556
Yeah. he means his real etchings.

302
00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:46.084
Okay? He collects stolen art.
uses it as collateral.

303
00:18:47.126 --> 00:18:48.521
What kind of art?

304
00:18:48.545 --> 00:18:52.691
I don't know. like. you know.
antiquities. priceless shit.

305
00:18:52.715 --> 00:18:55.069
- Where does he keep it?
- In his house.

306
00:18:55.093 --> 00:18:56.904
The house that he just invited us to?

307
00:18:56.928 --> 00:18:58.720
Yes. a horrible place.

308
00:19:01.099 --> 00:19:02.684
Why'd you stop?

309
00:19:03.434 --> 00:19:04.954
That's it.

310
00:19:04.978 --> 00:19:07.039
That's how we pay the Albanians.

311
00:19:07.063 --> 00:19:08.415
What?

312
00:19:08.439 --> 00:19:10.191
We're gonna rob him.

313
00:19:13.111 --> 00:19:14.821
