314
00:19:15.822 --> 00:19:17.508
Please! Give me more time.

315
00:19:17.532 --> 00:19:21.095
No. I'm triggering the Red Notice.
This is a manhunt now.

316
00:19:21.119 --> 00:19:22.847
"Womanhunt".
Anyway. we have to find them.

317
