343
00:20:57.924 --> 00:21:00.152
I mean. if Interpol...

344
00:21:00.176 --> 00:21:02.363
Besnik.

345
00:21:02.387 --> 00:21:04.222
Bring me all the money.

346
00:21:16.609 --> 00:21:17.777
Yeah.

347
00:21:19.487 --> 00:21:22.615
- They're in Monte Carlo.
- Monte Carlo.

348
00:21:30.665 --> 00:21:32.583
Pleasure doing business with you.

349
00:21:43.886 --> 00:21:46.556
You guys are going to love Monte Carlo.

350
00:21:50.810 --> 00:21:52.687
<i>All right. just get your things. we're going.</i>

351
00:21:53.438 --> 00:21:54.665
We've got to get out of town.

352
00:21:54.689 --> 00:21:56.417
No.

353
