368
00:22:30.391 --> 00:22:32.619
This is the only way out
of our situation. okay?

369
00:22:32.643 --> 00:22:35.873
I am doing this plan tonight.

370
00:22:35.897 --> 00:22:39.168
I am doing it. I am... I am...

371
00:22:39.192 --> 00:22:43.172
fu...

372
00:22:43.196 --> 00:22:44.298
You can't even say "fucking."

373
00:22:44.322 --> 00:22:48.719
Yes. I f...

374
00:22:48.743 --> 00:22:50.012
Stop breathing into the "fu."

375
00:22:50.036 --> 00:22:53.289
- Fuck. We're fucking doing it. Fuck!
- Brilliant.

376
00:22:54.540 --> 00:22:56.727
Looks like we're fucking doing it.

377
00:22:56.751 --> 00:22:58.544
You can shut your fucking cake hole. too.

378
00:23:00.797 --> 00:23:04.485
I'm looking for two women
who may have checked in recently.

379
00:23:04.509 --> 00:23:06.094
May I speak to your manager?

380
00:23:08.262 --> 00:23:10.115
Fuck.

381
00:23:10.139 --> 00:23:11.950
Fuck.

382
00:23:11.974 --> 00:23:14.328
Excuse me. hi.

383
00:23:14.352 --> 00:23:18.332
I am going to a black tie event tonight.
and I need a fucking dress. so...

384
00:23:18.356 --> 00:23:21.001
- Okay.
- I'm sorry. I-I...

385
00:23:21.025 --> 00:23:23.879
That wasn't directed at you.

386
00:23:23.903 --> 00:23:26.882
I-I-I recently learned to curse and...

387
00:23:26.906 --> 00:23:29.951
Good for you. I will go get the concierge.

388
00:23:35.164 --> 00:23:36.374
Big event this evening?

389
00:23:38.501 --> 00:23:40.729
Very. Sorry...

390
00:23:40.753 --> 00:23:42.463
- if you heard me curse.
- No.

391
00:23:43.047 --> 00:23:46.342
And. are you. are you
attending alone. or...?

392
00:23:47.552 --> 00:23:48.904
No. thank you.

393
00:23:48.928 --> 00:23:50.114
Excuse me?

394
00:23:50.138 --> 00:23:53.283
I mean. you seem very nice. but I've got
a lot going on right now.

395
00:23:53.307 --> 00:23:56.870
